modules.description: This module handles creation and manipulation of polymorphic 2D grids with precise coordinate access, supporting transformations like rotation and directional traversal. It operates on abstract grid structures containing arbitrary values, using integer coordinate pairs for positioning, and includes specialized utilities for character-based grids read from input streams. Functions for neighbor-aware computations, predicate-based position searches, and grid folding make it suitable for tasks like maze generation, cellular automata, or image processing workflows.
